    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted given the standardised ASTM F1717 protocol and medium model risk level. The validation activity provides extensive empirical support across two laboratories with N=11 constructs, and all quantitative acceptance bounds are satisfied (E/uval_max=1.61 < 1.96; max QoI difference 7.3% < 10%). The FEA modeling framework is judged credible for the stated COU.",
